48 by mutual agreement pursuant to Article 20 of Chapter 160A of the General Statutes and with
49 the written consent of the landowner, assign exclusive planning and development regulation
50 jurisdiction under this Chapter for the entire parcel to any one of those local governments. Such
51 a mutual agreement government, the following shall apply:
