31 "§ 160D-1403. Appeals of decisions on subdivision plats.
32 (a) When a subdivision regulation adopted under this Chapter provides that the decision
33 whether to approve or deny a preliminary or final subdivision plat is quasi-judicial, then that
34 decision of the board is subject to review by the superior court by a proceeding in the nature of
35 certiorari. G.S. 160D-406 and this section apply to those appeals.
