28 this section:
29 (1) The person has an ownership, leasehold, or easement interest in, or possesses
30 an option or contract to purchase the property that is the subject matter of a
31 final and binding decision made by an administrative official charged with
32 applying or enforcing a land development regulation.
33 (2) The person was a development permit applicant before the decision-making
