35 (3) The person was a development permit applicant who is aggrieved by a final
36 and binding decision of an administrative official charged with applying or
37 enforcing a land development regulation.
38 (4) An association, organization, society, or entity whose membership is
39 comprised of an individual or entity identified in subdivision (2) or (3) of this
40 subsection.
41 …
42 (g) Definitions. – The definitions definition of "development permit" in G.S. 143-755
43 shall apply in this section."
